'''Angela''' is a friend of [[Zola Grey Shepherd]].

==History==
Angela came over to Zola's house on Dia de los Muertos. They had their faces painted in preparation for a parade their school was doing. Meredith then took them both to school.

==Relationships==
===Friendships===
She is friends with [[Zola Grey Shepherd]].
